001
002package com.commercetools.api.predicates.query;
003
004public interface NotEqualPredicateBuilder<T, TValue> extends ComparablePredicateBuilder<T, TValue> {
005    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isNot(final TValue value) {
006        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_NOT, value);
007    }
008
009    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isNotVar(final String variable) {
010        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_NOT, VariableQueryPredicate.of().constant(variable));
011    }
012}
